# Fake News Detection using NLP

This project detects fake news articles using NLP and machine learning. It uses a TF-IDF vectorizer and a Passive Aggressive Classifier.

## Features
- Text preprocessing and TF-IDF feature extraction
- Fake news detection using Passive Aggressive Classifier
- Accuracy and confusion matrix for evaluation

## Requirements
